<P>
I'd like to thank CBS for its wonderful documentary, "The Moon Above, the Earth 
Below." The program's computer simulations were informative while Dan Rather 
and Charles Kuralt are also to be commended for their fine commentary. This is 
the type of programming that we need to see more often. 
</P>
<P>
Indi Trehan, Mission Viejo 
</P>
