Philharmonic. 
</P>
<P>
Glazunov: Violin Concerto; Oscar Shumsky, violin: Neeme Jarvi/Scottish National 
Orchestra. 
</P>
<P>
Lutoslawski: "Chain 2": Partita; Stravinsky: Violin Concerto: Anne-Sophie 
Mutter, violin: Witold Lutoslawski/BBC Symphony (Lutoslawski); Paul 
Sacher/Philharmonia Orchestra (Stravinsky). 
</P>
<P>
Mozart: Horn Concertos; Lowell Greer, horn: Nicholas McGegan/Philharmonia 
