CONSTRUCTION IS COMPLETED ON OXNARD BUSINESS CENTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Construction has been completed on Plaza Del Norte Business Center in Oxnard. 
The $8-million project is located on 6.85 acres at the Ventura (101) Freeway 
near Rose Avenue. 
</P>
<P>
The project, a development of McLachlan Investment Co. of Ventura, was designed 
by Ware &amp; Malcomb Architects's Woodland Hills office and encompasses 99,000 
square feet of space. 
</P>
