<P>
Photo, Checking for bacterial growth and monitoring water levels are routine 
for Dawn White, water quality supervisor at new lab of firm that supplies 
Rosemead, El Monte, San Gabriel, Duarte, Bradbury, San Marino, Temple City and 
Baldwin Hills. LOU MACK / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
</P>
