<SUBJECT>
<P>
FODOR, EUGENE; MUSICIANS; DRUG ABUSE; DRUG ARRESTS -- MASSACHUSETTS; BURGLARIES 
-- MASSACHUSETTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA073089-0141 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 88771 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 30, 1989, Sunday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
